        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
            Northern Ireland Retail Movement Scheme privacy notice
        </h1>

        <p>This privacy notice explains the process for traders that apply to move agri-food retail goods between Great Britain and Northern Ireland under the Windsor Framework via the Northern Ireland Retail Movement Scheme.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Who collects your personal data</h2>

        <p>The Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (Defra) is the controller for the personal data we collect. Defra's address is</p>
        <p>
